   <h2>CERIT-SC zve uživatele na PRACE a IT4Innovations Workshop v Ostravě </h2>
   

    <div class="news-teaser"></div>
    <div class="news-text"><p>CERIT-SC invites all MetaCentrum users to PRACE workshop &quot;Access to  computing resources and HPC services for the Czech Republic&quot;, which will  take place on May 7, 2013 in Business Incubator of VSB &ndash; Technical  University of Ostrava, Studentská 6202/17, room 332, 3rd floor.<br />
<br />
The aim of the workshop is to introduce the possibility of utilization  of the high performance computing resources to the Czech research  community. <a href="http://www.it4i.cz/files/130417_prace_program.pdf" target="_blank">Program</a></p>
<p>Participation is free of charge. Workshop is held in Czech language. <a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/13LuZB8mwV9wrHU-1-ZKTW5SpVqQRfPZ91YZDRUYNiqE/viewform" target="_blank">Registration form</a></p>
